\zoli1 \bd Igihe c’ubutumire kiriko kirahita twinjire mu muryango ucuguruye; umuco ugiye gutana n’umwiza, injira, injira wew’usigaye, n\bd*\bd ibwo butumire Umwami \bd*\bd Adutumira\bd*\bd .\bd*
